V'''Theodor Hermann Sternberg''' (January 5, 1878, [[Berlin]] - April 18, 1950, [[Tokyo]]) was a [[German people|German]] [[Jurisprudence|legal philosopher]] serving as a [[O-yatoi gaikokujin|foreign advisor]] in [[Meiji period]] [[Japan]], where he was an important contributor to the development of [[Civil law (legal system)|civil law]] in Japan.\u000a\u000a==Biography==\u000aSternberg served as an instructor at [[Tokyo Imperial University]] from 1913 to 1918. He also lectured on occasion at [[Meiji University]], and other major Japanese universities, speaking on civil law, [[criminal law]] and jurisprudence.\u000a\u000aHe later served as a consultant to the {{nihongo|[[Ministry of Justice (Japan)]]|[[:ja:\u53f8\u6cd5\u7701|\u53f8\u6cd5\u7701]] |''Shih\u014dsh\u014d''}} in 1918 and from 1922-1925, where he helped oversee the implementation of the Japanese legal codes.\u000a\u000a== Literary works ==\u000a* ''Allgemeine Rechtslehre'', 2 Vols. 1904\u000a* ''Einführung in die Rechtswissenschaft'', 1912\u000a* ''Der Begriff der Philosophie'', 1933\u000a\u000a==References==\u000a* Anna Bartels-Ishikawa: ''Theodor Sternberg - einer der Begründer des Freirechts in Deutschland und Japan.'' Duncker & Humboldt, Berlin 1998, ISBN 978-3-428-09228-4 (German)\u000a\u000a== External links ==\u000a* [http://www.duncker-humblot.de/?mnu=1100&cmd=1105&tid=47&typ=1101&did=29831 Duncker & Humblot - Gesamtverzeichnis - Bartels-Ishikawa, Anna - Theodor Sternberg -<!-- bot-generated title -->] at www.duncker-humblot.de (German)\u000a* [http://venus.unive.it/aistug/sunti/savona/losano.html AISTUGIA Il "diritto libero" di Theodor Sternberg dalla Germania al Giappone del primo Novecento<!-- bot-generated title -->] at venus.unive.it (Italian)\u000a* [http://www.francoangeli.it/riviste/Scheda_Riviste.asp?IDArticolo=16842&Tipo=Articolo%20PDF SOCIOLOGIA DEL DIRITTO - Il diritto libero di Theodor Sternberg dalla Germania al Giappone<!-- bot-generated title -->] at www.francoangeli.it (Italian)\u000a\u000a{{Authority control}}\u000a\u000a{{DEFAULTSORT:Sternberg, Theodor}}\u000a[[Category:German philosophers]]\u000a[[Category:German jurists]]\u000a[[Category:Foreign advisors to the government in Meiji-period Japan]]\u000a[[Category:Foreign educators in Japan]]\u000a[[Category:German expatriates in Japan]]\u000a[[Category:Philosophers of law]]\u000a[[Category:1878 births]]\u000a[[Category:1950 deaths]]\u000a[[Category:Writers from Berlin]]\u000a[[Category:German male writers]]\u000a\u000a\u000a{{Germany-law-bio-stub}}
